## How this report was generated

- Benchmarks run by the Pylox Forge pipeline against the live deployment endpoint
- Academic tests: `lm-evaluation-harness` (EleutherAI)
- Domain tests: `LegalBench` / `MedQA` / `FinanceBench` / `HumanEval` as appropriate
- LLM judge: local `gpt-oss-120b` (no third-party API touched)
- All client data stayed on Pylox hardware

*Reproducible — all inputs saved at `clients/{{ client }}/benchmark/results.json`.*
